## Project Title

GBDA302 Week 9 Example 3

---

## Authors

Fei Fei Chen

---

## Description

Allows players to jump over blocks and can toggle features like Moon Gravity and showing hitblocks in the debug menu. The menu can be visible and hidden by pressing the H button allowing users to access and toggle those features.

## Learning Goals

Learning Goals:

- Creating a debug screen menu
- Being able to toggle settings for a specific outcome
- Showing and hiding the debug screen menu

---

## Assets

There is sound effects and music uploaded in assets and images for the game.

